  <bodyText><![CDATA[<p><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13094125/summer-rewarding-838x330.jpg?width=207&amp;height=21" alt="rewarding walking holidays" data-udi="umb://media/4a93189bb8894c69b3aa7061556a47ff" /></p>
<p>Walk this way to a rewarding holiday. Our walking holidays in Europe take you off the beaten path, giving you a deeper understanding of your chosen location and a rewarding sense of achievement at the end of each day’s walk. Reward yourself with a spa treatment or dip in the jacuzzi. Because these boots were made for walking, but not without a celebratory glass of wine (or two) at the end of the trail.</p>
<p> </p>
<h2>Rewarding walking destinations</h2>
<p>If you're looking for an adventure that will leave your footprints on some of Europe's most beautiful landscapes, look no further. These rewarding walking destinations have it all - from stunning scenery to delicious cuisine, rich culture to beautiful landscapes.</p>
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h2><a data-udi="umb://document/08db820246524b63b3bfadde3a69e4f2" href="/{localLink:umb://document/08db820246524b63b3bfadde3a69e4f2}" title="Kandersteg">Kandersteg, Switzerland</a></h2>
<p><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13094136/kandersteg.jpg?width=500&amp;height=301" alt="kandersteg walking holiday" data-udi="umb://media/af7db8f10c384b19bb97ad6e23b45ce4" /></p>
<p><strong>Best for</strong> beautiful mountain scenery, and moderate and challenging walks.</p>
<p><strong>What our experts say...</strong></p>
<p>With breath-taking scenery from any trail, Kandersteg has plenty of rewarding views to enjoy regardless of the level of walk you decide to tackle. The attractive, relaxed and friendly village has plenty of trails around and above the village, including trails with views over the dazzling blue Lake Oeschinen and wildly beautiful Gastern Valley. </p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h2><a data-udi="umb://document/4c9fc09241f14e3c80acb89b5c9226dd" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4c9fc09241f14e3c80acb89b5c9226dd}" title="Selva">Selva, Italy </a></h2>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/4c9fc09241f14e3c80acb89b5c9226dd" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4c9fc09241f14e3c80acb89b5c9226dd}" title="Selva"><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13094137/sellajoch_sella-dolomitesvalgardena-1.jpg?width=173&amp;height=21" alt="selva walking holidays" data-udi="umb://media/10785ee3baa944148b71a55f3acce9d5" /></a></p>
<p><strong>Best for</strong> mountain views, family-friendly walks, and restaurants.</p>
<p><strong>What our experts say....</strong></p>
<p>There are many rewarding trails with spectacular views of the Dolomites and surrounding mountains, as well as tasty local food and wine. <a rel="noopener" href="https://www.valgardena-active.com/en/summer" target="_blank" title="Val Gardena Active Programme">The Val Gardena Active programme</a> has lots of fun activities for kids and teens. There's plenty of family-friendly walks, too. Set off together in search of postcard views, mountain wildlife, and adrenaline-pumping activities.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h2><a data-udi="umb://document/2735e2389f7c411cb3061226ce7548d1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2735e2389f7c411cb3061226ce7548d1}" title="Chamonix">Chamonix, France</a></h2>
<p><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13094138/chamonix.jpg?width=86&amp;height=21" alt="Chamonix" data-udi="umb://media/39769d15c61243efa8d7430a7314f62a" /></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>Best for </strong></span>postcard views, mountain wildlife, and adrenaline-pumping activities.</p>
<p><strong>What our experts say...</strong></p>
<p>If you're an active person, Chamonix will be the place for you. This rewarding resort offers many outdoor activities, including horse-riding and summer tobogganing. Head up to the Mer de glacier and take in some incredible views, then enjoy the journey back to town on the Montenvers railway.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h2><a data-udi="umb://document/5b2012f465d44823b6f9ba4c3b40fd4b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/5b2012f465d44823b6f9ba4c3b40fd4b}" title="Obergurgl">Obergurgl, Austria</a></h2>
<p><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13094139/obergurgl.jpg?width=204&amp;height=21" alt="obergurgl walking holidays" data-udi="umb://media/07559522c41b444ba0ee7f828ee6df29" /></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>Best for</strong> high alpine walking, wildlife and challenging walks.</span></p>
<p><strong>What our experts say...</strong></p>
<p>From the moment you arrive at this peaceful, alpine village and begin exploring the region's renowned hiking trails, it will be clear that this is the real Austria. The crisp mountain air and rich flora make it a rewarding place for nature lovers.</p>
</div>
</div>
<p> </p>
<div>
<h2 style="text-align: left;">Rewarding hotels</h2>
<p>We've selected the best hotels for a rewarding stay. Enjoy exceptional service, comfortable rooms and well-appointed amenities to make every moment truly memorable.</p>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<p><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/6f82021d14244f34943a16504c45664d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/6f82021d14244f34943a16504c45664d}" title="Hotel Der Bar">Der Bär, Austria</a></strong></p>
<p><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13071408/infinity-pool-with-views-to-wilder-kaiser.jpg?width=107&amp;height=21" alt="hotel der bar" data-udi="umb://media/471544afad7749cab9881e2a6226004d" /></p>
<p>This lifestyle and wellness hotel has an indoor pool, new sauna area and relaxation room, where you’ll get to enjoy unique, rewarding views to the Wilder Kaiser from the extensive panorama windows.</p>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/da18898c2b41431b907c91a66c4f4fc3" href="/{localLink:umb://document/da18898c2b41431b907c91a66c4f4fc3}" title="Hotel Rodella"><strong>Hotel Rodella, Italy</strong></a></p>
<p><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13076314/ita_selv_rode_01.jpg?width=104&amp;height=21" alt="hotel rodella" data-udi="umb://media/ade46e0498a94812a08016d7871f016f" /></p>
<p>This charming hillside hotel has fantastic views across the mountains and valley. Ideal for those who want to relax and unwind, or those who want to see the routes of their walks before they take them, it is a wonderful place to escape and relax.</p>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/e60e4140f1684d508d02b12990b6014a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e60e4140f1684d508d02b12990b6014a}" title="Hotel Edelweiss &amp; Gurgl"><strong>Edelweiss and Gurgl, Austria</strong></a></p>
<p><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13090380/eg-spa-ruheraum20191121_0187.jpg?width=195&amp;height=21" alt="edelweiss and gurgl hotel" data-udi="umb://media/112ae721a1384bdda7723cd1361eec41" /></p>
<p>This beautiful family-run hotel is perfect for those who want to enjoy a stunning mountain setting. It has superb spa facilities including an indoor/ outdoor pool, whirlpool, sauna, and exclusive in-house fitness club.</p>
<p> </p>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<p><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/d320f7c55a8d48bba0ae2db24d14b8dc" href="/{localLink:umb://document/d320f7c55a8d48bba0ae2db24d14b8dc}" title="Hotel Le Cottage">Hotel Le Cottage, France</a></strong></p>
<p><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13082713/candecottage1186-modifier.jpg?width=125&amp;height=21" alt="hotel le cottage" data-udi="umb://media/0ce99fc0967649d38df469447e58b8fd" /></p>
<p>Le Cottage is a traditional hotel that offers guests spectacular views of the lake and surrounding mountains. You can reward yourself by relaxing in the spa and wellness facilities, which include a solarium, whirlpool and an outdoor swimming pool with fantastic views across the water.</p>
<p> </p>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/093bbc54785244aa9aa802856c0b18e8" href="/{localLink:umb://document/093bbc54785244aa9aa802856c0b18e8}" title="Grand Hotel Toplice"><strong>Grand Hotel Toplice, Slovenia</strong></a></p>
<p><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13089938/slovenia-toplice-260x138.jpg?width=147&amp;height=21" alt="grand hotel toplice" data-udi="umb://media/939ae1ae23c9403b8031e2a7541a0524" /></p>
<p>Boasting a prime setting on Lake Bled’s shore and just steps from the charming town centre, this hotel is the ultimate luxury getaway. Set amidst idyllic gardens with views of the mountains, it offers everything you need for an unforgettable holiday.</p>
</div>
<div> </div>
<div style="text-align: center;"></div>
<div style="text-align: center;">
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/3471b74e93f54f109e136e4d91626d89" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3471b74e93f54f109e136e4d91626d89}" title="Best Value Summer Holidays 2024" class="c-btn">View 2025 holiday Deals</a></p>
</div>
<p> </p>
<h2>Looking for more inspiration?</h2>
<p>Walk your way to a perfect holiday with us. We offer a range of options for all tastes, from relaxing resorts to destinations for foodies and surprise-filled resorts.</p>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/8f01b61468784dcaa43c28a175d0b07a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/8f01b61468784dcaa43c28a175d0b07a}" title="Appetising walking holidays">Appetising</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13094131/summer-appetisizing-501x300.jpg?width=500&amp;height=299.4011976047904" alt="appetising walking holidays" data-udi="umb://media/87d041ea3e06407ba628212066cd996d" /></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/2345192f0fb94242b7572aa227f073bb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2345192f0fb94242b7572aa227f073bb}" title="Surprising walking holidays">Surprising</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13094134/summer-suprising-501x300.jpg?width=500&amp;height=299.4011976047904" alt="surprising walking holidays" data-udi="umb://media/86e74142f0c1406e8dae086ff4a4bf9a" /></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/8c744af040f54bf3a78285049d0d59c7" href="/{localLink:umb://document/8c744af040f54bf3a78285049d0d59c7}" title="Relaxing walking holidays">Relaxing</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13094132/summer-relaxing-501x300.jpg?width=500&amp;height=299.4011976047904" alt="relaxing walking holidays" data-udi="umb://media/097455c0dbb14e64ab60aab806965821" /></p>
</div>
<p> </p>
</div>
<h2 style="text-align: left;">Travel With Confidence</h2>
<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">When you choose an Inghams holiday, you can travel with confidence. We’re here to take the stress out of travelling. We’ve put extra measures in place for your peace of mind. We’ll help keep both you and your money safe.</span></p>
<p><img style="width: 916px; height: 231px; float: left;" src="/media/13095389/inghams-in-safe-hands-charcoal.png?width=916&amp;height=231&amp;mode=max" alt="in safe hands" data-udi="umb://media/afba17a916e84fcc848acce5dda4f9c4" /></p>
<p><strong>Terms and Conditions</strong></p>
<p>**<span>Up to two guided walks per week are included in the following resorts: </span><a data-udi="umb://document/594483304a5f4b47844b444df2c9d975" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/austria/austrian-tyrol/mayrhofen" title="Mayrhofen">Mayrhofen</a><span>, <a data-udi="umb://document/a71713291d5d4220aea1b806f34cd053" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a71713291d5d4220aea1b806f34cd053}" title="Seefeld">Seefeld</a>, </span><a data-udi="umb://document/ab49d5977a794ec7952da3e3d5adf48b" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/austria/saalbach-hinterglemm" title="Saalbach &amp; Hinterglemm">Saalbach &amp; Hinterglemm</a><span>, </span><a data-udi="umb://document/2735e2389f7c411cb3061226ce7548d1" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/france/chamonix" title="Chamonix">Chamonix</a><span>, </span><a data-udi="umb://document/a95b5199e8e04283bf8eeeabb42715fc" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/france/morzine" title="Morzine">Morzine</a><span>, </span><a data-udi="umb://document/604dbba59ac64320ab6e9f1e89231a4c" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/italy/lake-garda/limone" title="Limone">Limone</a><span>, <a data-udi="umb://document/c5c478381e04431da3f69d8364215ae7" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c5c478381e04431da3f69d8364215ae7}" title="Merano">Merano</a>,<a data-udi="umb://document/4c9fc09241f14e3c80acb89b5c9226dd" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4c9fc09241f14e3c80acb89b5c9226dd}" title="Selva"> Selva</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/b45a359445114107972cbb2b00be85ae" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b45a359445114107972cbb2b00be85ae}" title="Champoluc" data-anchor="#">Champoluc</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/de185d9ae756482295e4f069ba3a7aaf" href="/{localLink:umb://document/de185d9ae756482295e4f069ba3a7aaf}" title="Cervinia">Cervinia</a>, </span><a data-udi="umb://document/9b6cf6eac79541f5850e141e41a071ab" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/slovenia/kranjska-gora" title="Kranjska Gora">Kranjska Gora</a><span>, </span><a data-udi="umb://document/0fe9200934b24cd49d20e1cea080f5da" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/switzerland/bernese-oberland/grindelwald" title="Grindelwald">Grindelwald</a><span>, </span><a data-udi="umb://document/dd4c4793225641fcb24c0918a33714b3" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/switzerland/bernese-oberland/wengen" title="Wengen">Wengen</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/2e09d5bd5fae466db4b3c37d49150722" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/switzerland/zermatt" title="Zermatt">Zermatt, </a><a data-udi="umb://document/cad35d37f73d435087041e35025d1da8" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cad35d37f73d435087041e35025d1da8}" title="Funchal">Funchal</a> and <a data-udi="umb://document/f6d745a0efdf44b5b28bcd4bee55dbb1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f6d745a0efdf44b5b28bcd4bee55dbb1}" title="Canico">Caniço</a><span>. </span><span>All walks are subject to availability of local guides, weather conditions and maximum numbers. Where we cannot confirm your preferred option in resort, we will endeavour to offer an alternative subject to the above conditions. </span></p>
<p> </p>]]></bodyText>
